              {
                "name": "Description",
                "typeId": "9b8f-694b-e5e-b573",
                "$text": "This model can be attached to the following units:\n\n■ ASSAULT INTERCESSOR SQUAD\n■ BLADEGUARD VETERAN SQUAD\n■ COMPANY HEROES\n■ INTERCESSOR SQUAD\n■ STERNGUARD VETERAN SQUAD\n■ TACTICAL SQUAD"
